{"pageProps":{"articleData":[{"pk_df_blog_page_id":131,"blog_content":"<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 18px;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul's confusion about COVID protocols.</strong></span><br>       <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 18px;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul's COVID Journey: Chapter 1                  </strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">Rahul and Rajeev are cousins. They are 13 and 17 respectively. Rahul is a little confused about what he must and mustn’t do during the pandemic. Rajeev helps him figuring out his dilemma. Let’s hear their conversation!</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> But why is everyone sharing information on social media regarding oxygen supplies?</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> Because, Rahul, the country is facing a serious shortage of medical supplies including the provision of oxygen. The ones affected by COVID are suffering due to this shortage and people are trying to help those in need by sharing information they have gathered and verified! It’s kind of a noble cause, actually. We should do it too.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> Can’t the affected people take oxygen from hospitals and nursing homes near them?</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> Several hospitals and nursing homes are facing a crisis due to the massive inflow of COVID patients in the past month. In this situation, what would your near and dear ones do other than asking for help?</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> Oh, I get it. I’m relieved that the vaccines have been made. Now we can take it and lead a normal life again!</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> The vaccines have been administered to many citizens across the country. But for the vaccines to reach youngsters, there is still time. First, we are securing the ones with lower immunity.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul: </strong>My parents want to get vaccinated. How can they do that?</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> They can register</span> <a href=\"https://www.cowin.gov.in/home\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">here</span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">or look for the same in their localities.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> I can’t wait to roam around mask-free after I take the vaccine!</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> Don’t dare do it! The vaccines, although tested are not 100% effective on every person. Even after administering the vaccine, we must continue to wear a mask and maintain social distancing. You can know more about the vaccine</span> <a href=\"https://www.gavi.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">here</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> But aren’t we safe with our immunity and the strength provided by the vaccine? Why then should we wear a mask?</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> We maybe safe from the strain of the virus. But our near ones might not be! It is for them that we must definitely maintain all the protocols and stay safe from the virus.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> I was thinking of convincing our parents to go for a vacation! What do you say?</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> It is really irresponsible of you to think this way, Rahul! People are being affected everyday and suffering from the talons of the deadly disease. We have to live responsibly. The government has also released some</span> <a href=\"https://inshorts.com/en/news/govt-releases-list-of-dos-and-donts-for-plasma-donation-amid-covid19-surge-1619360622862?utm_source=news_share\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">do’s and don’ts</span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">regarding several topics.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> But I see so many people travelling and having fun!</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> Every person is different. It maybe useless to make some people understand the devastating consequences of their actions, but you, Rahul, are a smart boy. You should know that this is not a vacation you’re on. You must be active and work positively by staying indoors and putting on a mask whenever you go out.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul: </strong>What should someone do if I they think they have caught it?</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> If someone</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">suffers from a common cold, cough, nausea, vomiting, shortness of breath and fatigue, they must isolate themselves and contact your doctor immediately.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">That’s how they can prevent the spread of the illness! There are</span> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/detailsid=com.healthsignz.consumer.tenet&hl=en_IN&gl=US\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">apps</span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">that allow everyone to take the test sitting at home.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">They can also get an</span> <a href=\"https://doctor365.co.in/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">online consultation</span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">from doctors.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> What else can I do to stay healthy? I really want to develop my immune system and fight the virus!</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> That’s easy. You must stay indoors, keep safe distance from others, put on a mask, go out only when necessary, wash your hands after regular intervals, use sanitizers, take your medication, drink lots of water, take necessary vitamins and stay positive.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> What about the money we use? Isn’t that capable of transmitting the disease?</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> It’s true. What we can do is try to use online modes of payment like</span> <a href=\"https://pay.google.com/intl/en_in/about/?gclid=Cj0KCQjwyZmEBhCpARIsALIzmnKvy1e5Augz4my4cbhnZlcvFHbDAxqm6OziEZeFrnAQDTBtdU63YusaAsTaEALw_wcB&gclsrc=aw.ds\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">Google Pay</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">,</span> <a href=\"https://www.phonepe.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">PhonePe</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">,</span> <a href=\"https://paytm.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">Paytm</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">, etc. whenever we can and definitely sanitize the notes or coins we bring home. Safety comes before anything!</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rahul:</strong> That seems so easy to follow! I will definitely do these and punch the virus away.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Rajeev:</strong> That’s great Rahul. I hope you will live responsibly from now on and provide a service to the society.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong><ins>IMPORTANT LINKS MENTIONED:</ins></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gavi.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">About the Vaccine</span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cowin.gov.in/home\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">Registration for the Vaccine</span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/detailsid=com.healthsignz.consumer.tenet&hl=en_IN&gl=US\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">At-home COVID tests</span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://inshorts.com/en/news/govt-releases-list-of-dos-and-donts-for-plasma-donation-amid-covid19-surge-1619360622862?utm_source=news_share\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">Do’s and Don’ts of Plasma Donation</span> </a>&nbsp;</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://doctor365.co.in/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 19.2;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\">Online Doctor's Consultation</span></a>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Please check out this</strong></span> <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1UpvilfxliO5U0MzwmiYHI8I8X5GZqaG7?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>Drive link</strong></span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14pt;font-family: Open Sans\", sans;\"><strong>to get valuable information on the availability of essential COVID supplies across several states.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n","blog_headline":"Rahul's COVID Journey: Chapter 1 ","user_email":"ups0408@gmail.com","user_insta":"https://instagram.com/upasana_ghosh?igshid=hld19oug325w","user_facebook":null,"user_linkedin":null,"user_name":"Upasana Ghosh","create_timestamp":"2021-04-27T09:54:10.000Z","header_img_path":"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1ko-7XuwM7uc7zK8xSsC8JwDV3u5s3Dhz"}],"id":"131"},"__N_SSG":true}